<p><strong>SCP-CN-1671</strong> 不夜城</p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thefox4869" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5228967); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5228967&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609720565" alt="thefox4869" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5228967)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thefox4869" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5228967); return false;">thefox4869</a></span></p>
<p><strong>图像来源：</strong> CC Search: <a href="https://search.creativecommons.org/photos/1ac2387c-e534-43d4-8504-8111d06e76ef">《Night City》</a><br />
<strong>图像作者：</strong> cyberborean<br />
<em>图像遵守CC BY-SA 2.0协议。</em></p>
<p><strong>CSS版头：</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/theme:black-highlighter-theme">黑色标记笔</a></p>
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
